            "question": "In resolving x\u00b2 / ((x-1)\u00b2(x+2)), the highest power factor is (x-1)\u00b2. For A/(x-1) + B/(x-1)\u00b2 + C/(x+2), B is calculated directly by cover-up with x=1. What about A?",
